com.soa.delegate.config
Class DelegateConfiguration

java.lang.Object
  com.soa.delegate.config.DynamicProperties
      com.soa.delegate.config.DelegateConfiguration
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class DelegateConfiguration
extends DynamicProperties
implements java.io.Serializable

This is a simple bean to provide a mechanism to specify the configuration of the Delegate without imposing any sort of property loading requirements. Specifically, this is used in the BaseJAXxxxDelegate class that customers can use as a base class to construct their own JAX/RPC or JAX-WS invocation frameworks.

Since:
6.0
